title: Sonata Arctica (Live in Finland) 2 CD Edition
description:
Live in Finland is a live album and DVD recorded by the Finnish power metal band Sonata Arctica. Live in Finland was recorded at Club Teatria in Oulu, Finland on April 15, 2011 during the "The Days Of Grays" World Tour, and was released on November 11, 2011. 
Enjoy!
And remember to buy it if you like it, You will be supporting your favorite artist!
